      "text": "I was proud to speak at the ribbon-cutting of the newest public library in the country! 📚\n\nKeizer Community Library has earned its official public library designation, and it will now join Oregon's cooperative library system, expanding access to books, materials, and resources https://t.co/9njptoEGBQ",
